Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:20.10,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若夢　回眸幾何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:31.69,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}你所製作的　玻璃飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:35.41,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}指尖一觸　寸心如割
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:39.66,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必不可少的　不再所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.48,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}至始至終　覆水難收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:47.34,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　僅需一滴　臉頰便能浸潤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.26,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀絞　雨恨雲愁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:55.67,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我還是對你　一無所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.72,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那些落淚　就此止泣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:03.52,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想與你　歡聲笑語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:07.86,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如此憧憬　如此嚮往　想像便形成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:11.72,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就能改變當下　於晴空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:16.00,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起出發吧　窗外的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.91,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}攜手與你共賞春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.47,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}黑雲已散　風光日霽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:25.05,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨後鏡花水月　依舊彩虹色映
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:31.67,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨過天晴的你　眼眸自知物理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.80,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不過我想讓你　所尋自己而已
